title: R.I.P. George H.W. Bush (1924 - 2018), 41st president of the United States
description:
George H.W. Bush, 41st president of the United States, husband of Barbara Bush, and father of George W. Bush, died November 30, 2018. We remember his life and legacy.

Read our obituary for George H.W. Bush and share your condolences: http://bit.ly/2SmgIcs
